law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 30, effective July 13, 1984. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 393, effective June 17, 1978. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2417c-7.
